title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 145] Synth Punk, New Wave, Punk Rock
description:
Merry Christmas to all of you guys and gals out there who are following my uploads! I wish you and your family all the best and here's my xmas gift to you. Another set of obscure and hard to find records to share and spread around. 
The Eyes lp is my absolute favorite. I am sure you'll enjoy it as much as I do.

Enjoy and seed!

Front Page - Qualified [1981]

Jonny Sevin - Jonny Sevin [1982]

The Eyes - Tube Vision [1980]

The Professionals - I Didn't See It Coming [1981]
